# React to Laravel Blade + Livewire Volt (Inline/Non-Class) Conversion Guide

## Overview

This guide covers converting React function components (non-class) to Laravel Blade templates with **Livewire Volt inline components** — the functional composition API (not the `new class extends Component` class style). Inline Volt components are written using free functions like `state()`, `computed()`, `on()`, and `mount()` imported from `Livewire\Volt\Volt`.

## Tech Stack

- **Laravel**: 12.x
- **Livewire**: 4.x
- **Livewire Volt**: 1.x (inline/functional style)
- **Alpine.js**: 3.x (client-only interactions)
- **Tailwind CSS**: 4.x

