## Event Handling

### onClick → wire:click

**React:**

```jsx
<button onClick={() => deleteItem(item.id)}>Delete</button>
```

**Blade:**

```blade
<button wire:click="deleteItem({{ $item['id'] }})">Delete</button>
```

---

### onClick with stopPropagation → wire:click.stop

**React:**

```jsx
<button onClick={(e) => { e.stopPropagation(); handleClick(); }}>Click</button>
```

**Blade:**

```blade
<button wire:click.stop="handleClick">Click</button>
```

---

### Form onSubmit + controlled inputs → wire:submit + wire:model

**React:**

```jsx
<form onSubmit={handleSubmit}>
    <input value={email} onChange={(e) => setEmail(e.target.value)} />
    <button type="submit">Submit</button>
</form>
```

**Blade:**

```blade
<form wire:submit="handleSubmit">
    <input wire:model="email" type="email" />
    <button type="submit">Submit</button>
</form>
```

Declare the action:

```php
<?php
use function Livewire\Volt\{state};

state(['email' => '']);

$handleSubmit = function () {
    // validate and process
    $this->validate(['email' => 'required|email']);
    // ...
};
?>
```

