## Routing & Navigation

### React Router → Laravel Web Routes

**React:**

```jsx
<Route path="/profile/:id" element={<ProfilePage />} />
```

**Laravel `routes/web.php`:**

```php
use App\Livewire\Pages\Profile;

Route::get('/profile/{id}', Profile::class)->name('profile.show');
```

### Route Params in Volt Component

```php
<?php
use function Livewire\Volt\{state, mount};

state(['userId' => null, 'user' => null]);

mount(function (int $id) {
    $this->userId = $id;
    $this->user   = \App\Models\User::findOrFail($id)->toArray();
});
?>
```

